Package universitysystem.research

Class ResearchPaper

java.lang.Object
universitysystem.research.ResearchPaper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<ResearchPaper>
public class ResearchPaper extends Object implements Comparable<ResearchPaper>
Class ResearchPaper presents a research paper within the system of university. Implements the Comparable interface,which provides sorting of articles by their identifiers. Class is interconnected with authors, citations and pages.
